item.title: CVE-2017-15893|2024-09-17T02:16:52.281Z -- synology -- synology%20file%20station
item.description: Directory traversal vulnerability in the SYNO.FileStation.Extract in Synology File Station before 1.1.1-0099 allows remote authenticated users to write arbitrary files via the dest_folder_path parameter.
